WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.880
Perplexity is like having a research assistant that reads the entire web and summarizes it for

00:04.880 --> 00:10.640
you. Ask any question, get a direct answer with sources. No more scrolling through 10 blue links.

00:10.640 --> 00:17.120
Pro Search digs deeper for complex research. It even has an OpenAI compatible API so your AI

00:17.120 --> 00:22.320
agents can search the web too. Free to start, upgrade anytime you need more. Search smarter,

00:22.320 --> 00:23.120
now you can fly.

